    `audience_profile_id` BIGINT COMMENT 'Foreign key linking to audience.audience_profile. Business justification: Households are the primary unit of Nielsen HUT (Households Using Television) linear measurement. Linking household to an audience_profile enables household-level audience measurement, co-viewing analy',
