    `average_revenue_per_user` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'Average monthly revenue generated by this household, calculated as total revenue divided by number of active months. Key metric for household value assessment. | Column average_revenue_per_user (DECIMAL(10,2)) in subscriber.household',
    `billing_cycle_day` STRING COMMENT 'Day of the month when the households recurring subscription charge is processed. Typically set at initial subscription and remains consistent. | Column billing_cycle_day (INT) in subscriber.household',
    `churn_risk_score` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'Predictive score (0.00 to 100.00) indicating the likelihood of this household cancelling their subscription in the next billing period. Generated by machine learning models based on engagement and payment patterns. | Column churn_risk_score (DECIMAL(5,2)) in subscriber.household',
    `city` STRING COMMENT 'City or municipality where the household is located. Used for geographic segmentation and local content availability. | Column city (STRING) in subscriber.household',
    `country_code` STRING COMMENT 'Three-letter ISO 3166-1 alpha-3 country code for the household location. Determines applicable content rights, pricing, and regulatory requirements. | Column country_code (STRING) in subscriber.household. Valid values are `^[A-Z]{3}$`',
    `created_at` TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'Medallion lineage tracking column for bronze->silver->gold tracing | Column created_at (TIMESTAMP) in subscriber.household',
    `created_timestamp` TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'Timestamp when this household record was first created in the data platform. Used for data lineage and audit purposes. | Column created_timestamp (TIMESTAMP) in subscriber.household',
