    `household_type` STRING COMMENT 'Classification of the household based on its composition and purpose. Determines applicable service tier rules and entitlement models. | Column household_type (STRING) in subscriber.household. Valid values are `individual|family|shared|business|institutional|trial`',
    `language_preference` STRING COMMENT 'Two-letter ISO 639-1 language code representing the households preferred content and interface language. Used for content recommendations and UI localization. | Column language_preference (STRING) in subscriber.household. Valid values are `^[a-z]{2}$`',
    `last_login_timestamp` TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'Timestamp of the most recent authentication event for any member of this household. Used for engagement tracking and inactive account identification. | Column last_login_timestamp (TIMESTAMP) in subscriber.household',
