    `mvpd_affiliation` STRING COMMENT 'Name of the MVPD or vMVPD provider if this household accesses content through a cable/satellite/virtual provider authentication. Used for TV Everywhere entitlement validation. | Column mvpd_affiliation (STRING) in subscriber.household',
