    `parental_control_pin` STRING COMMENT 'Encrypted PIN code required to access age-restricted content when parental controls are enabled. Stored in hashed format for security. | Column parental_control_pin (STRING) in subscriber.household',
    `payment_method_type` STRING COMMENT 'Type of payment instrument on file for this households subscription billing. Determines payment processing flow and retry logic. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: credit_card|debit_card|paypal|bank_transfer|gift_card|carrier_billing|app_store — 7 candidates stripped; promote to reference product] | Column payment_method_type (STRING) in subscriber.household',
    `postal_code` STRING COMMENT 'Postal or ZIP code for the household address. Used for geographic market (DMA) assignment and service availability determination. | Column postal_code (STRING) in subscriber.household',
