    `audio_quality_max` STRING COMMENT 'Maximum audio quality format available under this subscription plan (e.g., stereo, surround 5.1, Dolby Atmos, DTS:X). | Column audio_quality_max (STRING) in subscriber.subscription_plan. Valid values are `stereo|surround_5_1|dolby_atmos|dts_x`',
