    `billing_frequency` STRING COMMENT 'Frequency at which subscribers are billed for this plan (e.g., monthly, quarterly, annual, biannual, one-time, usage-based). | Column billing_frequency (STRING) in subscriber.subscription_plan. Valid values are `monthly|quarterly|annual|biannual|one_time|usage_based`',
