    `churn_risk_category` STRING COMMENT 'Assessed churn risk category for subscribers on this plan based on historical churn rate analysis (low, medium, high). | Column churn_risk_category (STRING) in subscriber.subscription_plan. Valid values are `low|medium|high`',
