    `content_library_scope` STRING COMMENT 'Defines the scope of content library access granted by this plan (e.g., full catalog, limited selection, premium content only, sports only, news only, kids only). | Column content_library_scope (STRING) in subscriber.subscription_plan. Valid values are `full|limited|premium_only|sports_only|news_only|kids_only`',
